text: Weißenburg in Bayern (; East Franconian: Weizzenburch; formerly also Weißenburg im Nordgau) is a German town in Middle Franconia. It is the capital of Weißenburg-Gunzenhausen. == References == Category:Towns in Bavaria Category:Weißenburg-Gunzenhausen Category:1290s establishments Category:1803 disestablishments
title: Weißenburg in Bayern
